'''味觉感受器'''是一种专司[[味觉|味觉]]的[[受体_(生物化学)|受体]]器官，包括诸如[[TAS2R16|TAS2R16]]及[[TAS2R38|TAS2R38]]等。

== 分类 ==
味觉感受器被分成两大类：
* 类型1，专司[[味觉#甜|甜味]]，从{{Gene|TAS1R1}}至{{Gene|TAS1R3}}。该分类下的感受器在2001年第一次被描述<ref name="pmid11509186">{{cite journal | author = Nelson G, Hoon MA, Chandrashekar J, Zhang Y, Ryba NJ, Zuker CS | title = Mammalian sweet taste receptors | journal = Cell | volume = 106 | issue = 3 | pages = 381–90 | pmid = 11509186 | doi = 10.1016/S0092-8674(01)00451-2 | url = | issn = |date=August 2001}}</ref>；
* 类型2，专司[[味觉#苦|苦味]]，包括从{{Gene|TAS2R1}}至{{Gene|TAS2R50}}，以及{{Gene|TAS2R60}}。该分类下的感受器在2000年第一次被描述<ref name="pmid10761934">{{cite journal | author = Adler E, Hoon MA, Mueller KL, Chandrashekar J, Ryba NJ, Zuker CS | title = A novel family of mammalian taste receptors | journal = Cell | volume = 100 | issue = 6 | pages = 693–702 | pmid = 10761934 | doi = 10.1016/S0092-8674(00)80705-9 | url =  | issn = |date=March 2000}}</ref>。

